"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-paula-radcliffe-olympics-2024-steven-van-de-velde-b2585577.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Paula Radcliffe made the controversial comments about Steven van de Velde in an interview ahead of the Olympics  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paula Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.999999993195388, \"rank\": 6.804507351219134e-09, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Paula Radcliffehas apologised for wishing theDutch beach volleyball playerwho was convicted of raping a 12-year-old girl \\\"the best of luck\\\" ahead of the ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9716012531974958, \"rank\": 0.029228808326441327, \"text\": \"Paula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Olympic runner said that Steven van de Velde \\\"should not be punished twice\\\".\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.999999993195388, \"rank\": 6.804507351219134e-09, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thevolleyball player pled guilty to raping the British childwhen he was 19 and wassentenced to four years in prison in 2016.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9910890762146131, \"rank\": 0.007454229480532931, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe was asked by Andrew Marr's LBC programme about the decision to allow Van de Velde to compete.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9089770332683919, \"rank\": 0.10013775991510232, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Marr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.1312895358970055e-11, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that it is a very dangerous line to go down given that we allow people who cheat in sport and take drugs in sport to then come back and compete,\\\" Radcliffe said in the interview.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9089770332683919, \"rank\": 0.10013775991510232, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was 19 at the time and he's served his jail time and it's a long time to carry on paying for that mistake for the rest of your life.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He may well have turned it around and completely repented.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You certainly hope.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that he is married now and has settled down.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck.\\\"\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde met the girl on Facebook, and flew to England to meet her with full knowledge of her age.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7659928074170215, \"rank\": 0.16909729086728628, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only served 12 months in a Dutch prison and has since returned to compete internationally.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's groups have condemned the decision to allow Van de Velde to compete at the Games, and criticised his selection by the Netherlands.The Timesreports the 29-year-old is staying at a different location rather than with the other competitors in the athletes' village.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other organisations, including the British Olympic Association would not have allowed the beach volleyball player onto their Olympic team because of their own safeguarding rules.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe however seemed to take back those comments, replying to a post criticising her on X, she said: \\\"I agree (that what she said was shocking) and can only apologise, that is not what I intended to say.\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2298, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9089770332683919, \"rank\": 0.10013775991510232, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I stress that it is not something that can be excused in any way.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was confused in my head and responding to the right to ban him from the Games and I do not know why I wished him luck.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Again I apologise.\\\"\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe added,reported by the BBC: \\\"I am mortified that I expressed it so badly and did not condemn the rape out loud.\\\"\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2716, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9089770332683919, \"rank\": 0.10013775991510232, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.831835459357458, \"rank\": 0.20187927156341862, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2890, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.3829479533013247e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_